Running the Project


1)  Backend Services
To start backend services, 
navigate to the folder infrastructure/ and run:
docker compose down
docker compose up --build


2)  Frontend
The frontend runs via Docker.
From the root of the frontend directory, execute:
docker build -t ft_transcendence_frontend .
docker run -p 8080:80 ft_transcendence_frontend

3) Then open your browser and go to:
http://localhost:8080



CLI USAGE
- to start the game:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/game/start \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "leftPlayer": { "alias": "Alice" },
    "rightPlayer": { "alias": "Bob" },
    "matchId": 1,
    "type": "CONSOLE"
  }'

- to stop the game:
curl http://localhost:3000/game/stop   

